	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ah, <delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />! <delay20 />Sei gegrüßt, <delay8 /><tag a="110" b="5" />!<pageBreak /><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Na so etwas.<delay20 /> Da war es wieder...<delay20 />
